<plot>From the interrogation room of Chicago's Metro Correctional Center, mob soldier turned federal witness Tommy Russo tells a tale of murder and deception in flashback sequences. "It was supposed to be easy money"... a perfectly planned mob insurance scam involving a half million in precious stones. What it became was a botched jewelry heist that resulted in the death of a cop and two security guards, and set off a deadly chain of events.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?552379</url></doc>
